Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:06.24,English,,0,0,0,,Imagine you have a giant circuit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:06.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:09.25,English,,0,0,0,,consisting of a battery, a switch, a light bulb,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:09.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:13.96,English,,0,0,0,,and two wires which are each 300,000 kilometers long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:13.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.95,English,,0,0,0,,That is the distance light travels in one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:19.61,English,,0,0,0,,So, they would reach out half way to the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:19.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:22.11,English,,0,0,0,,and then come back to be connected to the light bulb,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:22.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:24.27,English,,0,0,0,,which is one meter away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:24.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.31,English,,0,0,0,,Now, the question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.30,English,,0,0,0,,after I close this switch,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:30.27,English,,0,0,0,,how long would it take for the bulb to light up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:30.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:31.84,English,,0,0,0,,Is it half a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:31.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:32.80,English,,0,0,0,,one second,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:32.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.28,English,,0,0,0,,two seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:35.78,English,,0,0,0,,1/c seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:35.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:37.53,English,,0,0,0,,or none of the above.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:37.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:39.26,English,,0,0,0,,You have to make some simplifying assumptions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:39.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.72,English,,0,0,0,,about this circuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.63,English,,0,0,0,,like the wires have to have no resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:43.89,English,,0,0,0,,otherwise this wouldn't work
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:43.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.29,English,,0,0,0,,and the light bulb has to turn on immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.37,English,,0,0,0,,when current passes through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:50.82,English,,0,0,0,,But I want you to commit to an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:50.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.84,English,,0,0,0,,and put it down in the comments
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:53.72,English,,0,0,0,,so you can't say,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:53.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.71,English,,0,0,0,,oh yeah I knew that was the answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:57.90,English,,0,0,0,,when I tell you the answer later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:57.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:02.66,English,,0,0,0,,This question actually relates to how electrical energy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:02.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.13,English,,0,0,0,,get from a power plant to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:07.28,English,,0,0,0,,Unlike a battery,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:07.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:08.70,English,,0,0,0,,the electricity in the grid
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:08.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:11.88,English,,0,0,0,,comes in the form of alternating current, or AC,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:11.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:13.82,English,,0,0,0,,which means electrons in the power lines
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:13.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:15.55,English,,0,0,0,,are just wiggling back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:15.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.27,English,,0,0,0,,They never actually go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:21.34,English,,0,0,0,,So, if the charges don't come from the power plant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:21.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:22.60,English,,0,0,0,,to your home,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:22.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:26.03,English,,0,0,0,,how does the electrical energy actually reach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:26.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.43,English,,0,0,0,,When I used to teach this subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.43,0:01:30.81,English,,0,0,0,,I would say that power lines
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.43,0:01:30.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:33.41,English,,0,0,0,,are like this flexible plastic tubing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:33.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:36.74,English,,0,0,0,,and the electrons inside are like this chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:36.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.56,English,,0,0,0,,So, what a power station does,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:42.33,English,,0,0,0,,is it pushes and pulls the electrons back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:42.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:44.45,English,,0,0,0,,60 times a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:44.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:45.84,English,,0,0,0,,Now, at your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:45.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:48.23,English,,0,0,0,,you can plug in a device, like a toaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:48.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:49.68,English,,0,0,0,,which essentially means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:49.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.18,English,,0,0,0,,allowing the electrons to run through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:55.53,English,,0,0,0,,So when the power station pushes and pulls the electrons,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:55.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:59.77,English,,0,0,0,,well, they encounter resistance in the toaster element,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:59.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:03.13,English,,0,0,0,,and they dissipate their energy as heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:03.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.22,English,,0,0,0,,and so you can toast your bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.61,English,,0,0,0,,Now, this is a great story,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:07.94,English,,0,0,0,,I think it's easy to visualize,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:07.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.98,English,,0,0,0,,and I think my students understood it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.68,English,,0,0,0,,The only problem is, it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.53,English,,0,0,0,,For one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.89,English,,0,0,0,,there is no continuous conducting wire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.09,English,,0,0,0,,that runs all the way from a power station to your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.37,English,,0,0,0,,No, there are physical gaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.45,English,,0,0,0,,there are breaks in the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.61,English,,0,0,0,,like in transformers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:28.00,English,,0,0,0,,where one coil of wire is wrapped on one side,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:28.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.10,English,,0,0,0,,a different coil of wire is wrapped on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:32.72,English,,0,0,0,,So, electrons cannot possibly flow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:32.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.62,English,,0,0,0,,from one the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.92,English,,0,0,0,,Plus, if it's the electrons
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.46,English,,0,0,0,,that are carrying the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:41.12,English,,0,0,0,,from the power station to your device,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:41.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.63,English,,0,0,0,,then when those same electrons
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:44.44,English,,0,0,0,,flow back to the power station,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:44.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:47.14,English,,0,0,0,,why are they not also carrying energy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:47.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:50.51,English,,0,0,0,,back from your house to the power station?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:50.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:53.68,English,,0,0,0,,If the flow of current is two ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:53.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:58.24,English,,0,0,0,,then why does energy only flow in one direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:58.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.78,English,,0,0,0,,These are the lies you were taught about electricity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.32,English,,0,0,0,,that electrons themselves have potential energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.56,English,,0,0,0,,that they are pushed or pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.97,English,,0,0,0,,through a continuous conducting loop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:13.08,English,,0,0,0,,and that they dissipate their energy in the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:13.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.42,English,,0,0,0,,My claim in this video
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.27,English,,0,0,0,,is that all of that is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.66,English,,0,0,0,,So, how does it actually work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.33,English,,0,0,0,,In the 1860's and 70's,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.16,English,,0,0,0,,there was a huge breakthrough
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.95,English,,0,0,0,,in our understanding of the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.73,English,,0,0,0,,when Scottish physicist, James Clerk Maxwell,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.40,English,,0,0,0,,realized that light is made up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:36.72,English,,0,0,0,,of oscillating electric and magnetic fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:36.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:39.82,English,,0,0,0,,The fields are oscillating perpendicular to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:39.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.23,English,,0,0,0,,and they are in phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.18,English,,0,0,0,,meaning when one is at its maximum,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.75,English,,0,0,0,,so is the other wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.67,English,,0,0,0,,Now, he works out the equations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:50.57,English,,0,0,0,,that govern the behavior of electric and magnetic fields
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:50.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.37,English,,0,0,0,,and hence, these waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:52.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.38,English,,0,0,0,,those are now called Maxwell's equations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.27,English,,0,0,0,,But in 1883,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:04:00.31,English,,0,0,0,,one of Maxwell's former students, John Henry Poynting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:04:00.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:02.91,English,,0,0,0,,is thinking about conversation of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:02.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:07.40,English,,0,0,0,,If energy is conserved locally in every tiny bit of space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:07.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:10.17,English,,0,0,0,,well, then you should be able to trace the path
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:10.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:13.09,English,,0,0,0,,that energy flows from one place to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:13.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.62,English,,0,0,0,,So, think about the energy that comes to us from the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:19.77,English,,0,0,0,,during those eight minutes when the light is traveling,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:19.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.92,English,,0,0,0,,the energy is stored and being transmitted
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.85,English,,0,0,0,,in the electric and magnetic fields of the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:29.66,English,,0,0,0,,Now, Poynting works out an equation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:29.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:32.09,English,,0,0,0,,to describe energy flux,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:32.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:34.62,English,,0,0,0,,that is, how much electromagnetic energy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:34.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.68,English,,0,0,0,,is passing through an area per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.65,English,,0,0,0,,This is known as the Poynting vector
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.75,English,,0,0,0,,and it's given the symbol S.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:43.68,English,,0,0,0,,And the formula is really pretty simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:43.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:46.10,English,,0,0,0,,it's just a constant one over mu naught,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:46.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:48.23,English,,0,0,0,,which is the permeability of free space
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:48.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.35,English,,0,0,0,,times E X B.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.18,English,,0,0,0,,Now, E X B,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.26,English,,0,0,0,,is the cross product
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.81,English,,0,0,0,,of the electric and magnetic fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.20,English,,0,0,0,,Now, the cross product is just a particular way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.27,English,,0,0,0,,of multiplying two vectors together,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.80,English,,0,0,0,,where you multiply their perpendicular magnitudes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.12,English,,0,0,0,,and to find the direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:04.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:06.56,English,,0,0,0,,you put your fingers in the direction of the first vector,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:06.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.43,English,,0,0,0,,which in this case is the electric field,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.08,English,,0,0,0,,and curl them in the direction of the second vector,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:11.93,English,,0,0,0,,the magnetic fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:11.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.76,English,,0,0,0,,then your thumb points
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.60,English,,0,0,0,,in the direction of the resulting vector,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.42,English,,0,0,0,,the energy flux.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.55,English,,0,0,0,,So, what this shows us about light
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.68,English,,0,0,0,,is that the energy is flowing perpendicular
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.66,English,,0,0,0,,to both the electronic an the magnetic fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:29.16,English,,0,0,0,,And it's in the same direction as the light is traveling,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:29.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.76,English,,0,0,0,,so this makes a lot of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.61,English,,0,0,0,,Light carries energy from its source
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.79,English,,0,0,0,,out to its destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.87,English,,0,0,0,,But the kicker is this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.46,English,,0,0,0,,Poynting's equation doesn't just work for light,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:46.75,English,,0,0,0,,it works anytime there are electric
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:46.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.24,English,,0,0,0,,and magnetic fields coinciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.08,English,,0,0,0,,Anytime you have electric and magnetic fields together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.61,English,,0,0,0,,there is a flow of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.65,English,,0,0,0,,and you can calculate using Poynting's vector.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.26,English,,0,0,0,,To illustrate this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,为了说明这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.91,English,,0,0,0,,let's consider a simple circuit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让我们考虑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:04.10,English,,0,0,0,,with a battery and a light bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:04.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,含有电池和灯泡的简单电路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:07.26,English,,0,0,0,,The battery by itself has an electric field
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:07.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,电池自身激发了一个电场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.30,English,,0,0,0,,but since no charges are moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是由于没有电荷移动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.05,English,,0,0,0,,there is no magnetic field
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以没有磁场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.93,English,,0,0,0,,so the battery doesn't lose energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,于是这块电池不损失能量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.13,English,,0,0,0,,When the battery is connected into the circuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当电池接入电路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:19.14,English,,0,0,0,,its electric field extends through the circuit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:19.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,其电场沿着电路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.84,English,,0,0,0,,at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以光速延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.69,English,,0,0,0,,This electric field pushes electrons around
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,电场推动周围的电子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:27.32,English,,0,0,0,,so they accumulate on some of the surfaces of the conductors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:27.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以它们在导体的某些表面聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.06,English,,0,0,0,,making them negatively charged,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,使导体带负电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.97,English,,0,0,0,,and are depleted elsewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,电子在其他地方较少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.48,English,,0,0,0,,leaving their surfaces positively charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些位置带正电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.15,English,,0,0,0,,These surface charges
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些表面电荷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:39.55,English,,0,0,0,,create a small electric field inside the wires,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:39.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在导线内部激发了微弱的电场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.44,English,,0,0,0,,causing electrons to drift
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,导致了电子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.84,English,,0,0,0,,preferentially in one direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,定向漂移运动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.05,English,,0,0,0,,Note that this drift velocity is extremely slow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,注意这种漂移的速度极其缓慢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.83,English,,0,0,0,,around a tenth of a millimeter per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大约只有 0.1 mm/s
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.73,English,,0,0,0,,But this is current,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是这就是电流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:52.85,English,,0,0,0,,well, conventional current
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:52.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,呃 传统上电流方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.22,English,,0,0,0,,is defined to flow opposite the motion of electrons,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,定义为电子运动的相反方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.65,English,,0,0,0,,but this is what's making it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是这就是电流产生的原理 （？）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.65,English,,0,0,0,,The charge on the surfaces of the conductors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,导体表面的电荷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.03,English,,0,0,0,,also creates an eclectic field outside the wires
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也在外部产生了电场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:07.28,English,,0,0,0,,and the current inside the wires
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:07.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而导线中的电流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.51,English,,0,0,0,,creates a magnetic field outside the wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在导线外产生了磁场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.81,English,,0,0,0,,So, now there is a combination
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以 现在导线周围
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.98,English,,0,0,0,,of electric and magnetic fields
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,的空间中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:17.22,English,,0,0,0,,in this space around the circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:17.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,既有电场也有磁场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.41,English,,0,0,0,,So, according to Poynting's theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,于是按照波印廷的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.58,English,,0,0,0,,energy should be flowing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能量会（在其中）流动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.12,English,,0,0,0,,and we can work out the direction of this energy flow
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,利用右手定则
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:26.06,English,,0,0,0,,using the right hand rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:26.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们可以计算能流的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:27.79,English,,0,0,0,,Around the battery for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:27.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,例如在电池周围
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:29.73,English,,0,0,0,,the electric field is down
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:29.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,电矢量向下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.53,English,,0,0,0,,and the magnetic field is into the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而磁矢量垂直屏幕向外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:35.54,English,,0,0,0,,So, you find the energy flux is to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:35.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以你会发现能流是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:37.74,English,,0,0,0,,away from the battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:37.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,向右离开电池的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.81,English,,0,0,0,,In fact, all around the battery,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,事实上 在电池周围
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:43.56,English,,0,0,0,,you'll find the energy is radially outwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:43.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你会发现每处能量都在径向外流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:47.23,English,,0,0,0,,Energy is going out through the sides of the battery
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:47.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能量从电池侧面离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.12,English,,0,0,0,,into the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并进入电磁场中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.98,English,,0,0,0,,Along the wires, again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,沿着导线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.25,English,,0,0,0,,you can use the right hand rule
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:52.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以再次应用右手定则
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:55.34,English,,0,0,0,,to find the energy is flowing to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:55.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,得到能量向右流动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.17,English,,0,0,0,,This is true for the fields along the top wire
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这对位于上侧的导线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.05,English,,0,0,0,,and the bottom wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和下侧的导线都成立
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:00.94,English,,0,0,0,,But at the filament,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:00.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但在灯丝处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:04.82,English,,0,0,0,,the Poynting vector is directed in toward the light bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:04.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,波印廷矢量指向灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.20,English,,0,0,0,,So, the light bulb is getting energy from the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,故灯泡从电磁场中获得能量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.33,English,,0,0,0,,If you do the cross product,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你计算叉积
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:13.87,English,,0,0,0,,you find the energy is coming in from all around the bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:13.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你会发现能量从各个方向流向灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.44,English,,0,0,0,,It takes many paths from the battery to the bulb,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从电池到灯泡的路线不尽相同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.73,English,,0,0,0,,but in all cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不论哪种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.37,English,,0,0,0,,the energy is transmitted
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能量总是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.87,English,,0,0,0,,by the electric and magnetic fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,经由电磁场传输
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.17,English,,0,0,0,,- People seem to think that you're pumping electrons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.18,English,,0,0,0,,and that you're buying electrons or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:29.25,English,,0,0,0,,which is just so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:29.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:30.08,English,,0,0,0,,For most people,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:30.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.39,English,,0,0,0,,and I think to this day, it's quite counterintuitive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:35.28,English,,0,0,0,,to think that the energy is flowing through the space
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:35.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.84,English,,0,0,0,,around the conductor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.27,English,,0,0,0,,but the energy is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.49,English,,0,0,0,,which is traveling through the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:42.21,English,,0,0,0,,yeah, is going quite fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:42.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.11,English,,0,0,0,,- So, there are a few things to notice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.21,English,,0,0,0,,Even though the electrons go two ways
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.40,English,,0,0,0,,away from the battery and towards it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.14,English,,0,0,0,,by using the Poynting vector,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.45,English,,0,0,0,,you find that the energy flux only goes one way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.72,English,,0,0,0,,from the battery to the bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.70,English,,0,0,0,,This also shows it's the fields
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.12,English,,0,0,0,,and not the electrons that carry the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.74,English,,0,0,0,,- How far do the electrons go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.13,English,,0,0,0,,in this little thing you're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.54,English,,0,0,0,,they barely move,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.33,English,,0,0,0,,they probably don't move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.78,English,,0,0,0,,- Now, what happens if in place of a battery,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:13.58,English,,0,0,0,,we use an alternating current source?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:13.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:15.18,English,,0,0,0,,Well then, the direction of current
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:15.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.49,English,,0,0,0,,reverses every half cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:20.52,English,,0,0,0,,But this means that both the electric and magnetic fields
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:20.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.84,English,,0,0,0,,flip at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.28,English,,0,0,0,,so at any instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.61,English,,0,0,0,,the Poynting vector still points in the same direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.57,English,,0,0,0,,from the source to the bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:32.55,English,,0,0,0,,So the exact same analysis we used for DC
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:32.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.00,English,,0,0,0,,still works for AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.49,English,,0,0,0,,And this explains how energy is able to flow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.70,English,,0,0,0,,from power plants to home in power lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:40.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.77,English,,0,0,0,,Inside the wires,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.32,English,,0,0,0,,electrons just oscillate back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:47.09,English,,0,0,0,,Their motion is greatly exaggerated here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:47.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.73,English,,0,0,0,,But they do not carry the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.90,English,,0,0,0,,Outside the wires,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.15,English,,0,0,0,,oscillating eclectic and magnetic fields
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:56.13,English,,0,0,0,,travel from the power station to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:56.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.04,English,,0,0,0,,You can use the Poynting vector to check
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:01.42,English,,0,0,0,,that the energy flux is going in one direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:01.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:05.54,English,,0,0,0,,You might think this is just an academic discussion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:05.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.89,English,,0,0,0,,that you could see the energy as transmitted
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:11.40,English,,0,0,0,,either by fields or by the current in the wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:11.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.58,English,,0,0,0,,But that is not the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.26,English,,0,0,0,,and people learned this the hard way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.61,English,,0,0,0,,when they started laying undersea telegraph cables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:22.71,English,,0,0,0,,The first Trans Atlantic cable was laid in 1858.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:22.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.25,English,,0,0,0,,- It only worked for about a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.76,English,,0,0,0,,it never worked properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.42,English,,0,0,0,,- There are all kinds of distortions
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:28.33,English,,0,0,0,,when they try to send signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:28.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.49,English,,0,0,0,,- Enormous amounts of distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.65,English,,0,0,0,,They could work it at a few words per minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.84,English,,0,0,0,,- What they found was sending signals
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:37.22,English,,0,0,0,,over such a long distance under the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:37.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.48,English,,0,0,0,,the pulses became distorted and lengthened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:43.57,English,,0,0,0,,It was hard to differentiate dots from dashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:43.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:45.51,English,,0,0,0,,To account for the failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:45.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:47.92,English,,0,0,0,,there was a debate among scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:47.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.61,English,,0,0,0,,William Thomson, the future Lord Kelvin,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:53.39,English,,0,0,0,,thought electrical signals moved through submarine cables
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:53.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:56.12,English,,0,0,0,,like water flowing through a rubber tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:56.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.66,English,,0,0,0,,But others like Heaviside and Fitzgerald,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:01.24,English,,0,0,0,,argued it was the fields around the wires
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:01.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.72,English,,0,0,0,,that carried the energy and information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.01,English,,0,0,0,,And ultimately,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.44,English,,0,0,0,,this view proved correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.34,English,,0,0,0,,To insulate and protect the submarine cable,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.15,English,,0,0,0,,the central copper conductor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.95,English,,0,0,0,,had been coated in an insulator
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:16.67,English,,0,0,0,,and then encased in an iron sheath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:16.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:19.40,English,,0,0,0,,The iron was only meant to strengthen the cable,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:19.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.84,English,,0,0,0,,but as a good conductor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.90,English,,0,0,0,,it interfered with a propagation of electromagnetic fields
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:27.38,English,,0,0,0,,because it increased the capacitance of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:27.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:31.09,English,,0,0,0,,This is why today, most power lines are suspended high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:31.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.88,English,,0,0,0,,Even the damp earth acts as a conductor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.76,English,,0,0,0,,so you want a large insulating gap of air
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:39.36,English,,0,0,0,,to separate the wires from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:39.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.42,English,,0,0,0,,So, what is the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:45.95,English,,0,0,0,,to our giant circuit light bulb question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:45.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.68,English,,0,0,0,,Well, after I close the switch,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.80,English,,0,0,0,,the light bulb will turn on almost instantaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:54.09,English,,0,0,0,,in roughly 1/C seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:54.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:57.05,English,,0,0,0,,So, the correct answer is D.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:57.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.58,English,,0,0,0,,I think a lot of people imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.76,English,,0,0,0,,that the electric field needs to travel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.84,English,,0,0,0,,from the battery,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.16,English,,0,0,0,,all the way down the wire
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.98,English,,0,0,0,,which is a light second long,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:07.88,English,,0,0,0,,so it should take a second for the bulb to light up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:07.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:09.74,English,,0,0,0,,But what we've learned in this video
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:09.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:12.60,English,,0,0,0,,is it's not really what's happening in the wires
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:12.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.55,English,,0,0,0,,that matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:16.06,English,,0,0,0,,it's what happens around the wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:16.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.47,English,,0,0,0,,And the electric and magnetic fields
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.68,English,,0,0,0,,can propagate out through space
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:20.67,English,,0,0,0,,to this light bulb,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:20.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:24.87,English,,0,0,0,,which is only one meter away in a few nanoseconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:24.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.66,English,,0,0,0,,And so, that is the limiting factor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.11,English,,0,0,0,,for the light bulb turning on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.55,English,,0,0,0,,Now, the bulb won't receive
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:33.46,English,,0,0,0,,the entire voltage of the battery immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:33.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.77,English,,0,0,0,,it'll be some fraction,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.86,English,,0,0,0,,which depends on the impedance of these lines
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.91,English,,0,0,0,,and the impedance of the bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.24,English,,0,0,0,,Now, I asked several experts about this question,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.10,English,,0,0,0,,and got kind of different answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.78,English,,0,0,0,,but we all agreed on these main points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.76,English,,0,0,0,,So, I'm gonna put their analysis in the description
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:52.69,English,,0,0,0,,in case you want to learn more about this particular setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:52.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.79,English,,0,0,0,,If I get called out on it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:53.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.45,English,,0,0,0,,and people don't think it's real,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:58.31,English,,0,0,0,,we can definitely invest the resources
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:58.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:12:59.90,English,,0,0,0,,and string up some lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:12:59.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.18,English,,0,0,0,,and make our own power lines in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:03.36,English,,0,0,0,,- I think you're gonna get called out on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:03.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:06.28,English,,0,0,0,,- I agree, I think you're gonna get called out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:06.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.97,English,,0,0,0,,I think that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.59,English,,0,0,0,,- I think it's just kinda wild
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:14.53,English,,0,0,0,,that this is one of those things
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:14.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:16.07,English,,0,0,0,,that we use everyday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:16.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:18.44,English,,0,0,0,,that almost nobody thinks about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:18.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.65,English,,0,0,0,,or knows the right answer to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.42,English,,0,0,0,,These traveling electromagnetic waves around power lines
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:25.86,English,,0,0,0,,are really what's delivering your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:25.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
